SELECT DISTINCT ?organism ?taxon_commonname ?anatomicalentity ?gene_description ?anatomicalentityName ?anatomicalentity_label ?taxon_scientificname ?gene ?taxon WHERE { 
	?gene a orth:Gene .
	?gene genex:isExpressedIn ?anatomicalentity. # is expressed in
	?gene rdfs:label "APOC1" .
	?anatomicalentity a genex:AnatomicalEntity .
	?anatomicalentity rdfs:label ?anatomicalentityName .
	### Specifying species:
	?gene orth:organism ?organism . # in organism
	?organism obo:RO_0002162  ?taxon . # in taxon
	?taxon a up:Taxon .
	?taxon up:scientificName "Homo sapiens" .
	?taxon <http://purl.uniprot.org/core/scientificName> ?taxon_scientificname.
	?taxon <http://purl.uniprot.org/core/commonName> ?taxon_commonname.
	?anatomicalentity <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> ?anatomicalentity_label.
	?gene <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> ?gene_description.
}

PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>
PREFIX efo: <http://www.ebi.ac.uk/efo/EFO_0000399>
SELECT DISTINCT ?stage ?stageName ?stageDescription WHERE { 
	?stage rdf:type efo:EFO_0000399 .
	?stage rdfs:label ?stageName .
	?stage dcterms:description ?stageDescription .
	FILTER( CONTAINS(?stageName,"post-juvenile" )
}

PREFIX orth: <http://purl.org/net/orth#>
PREFIX genex: <http://purl.org/genex#>
PREFIX obo: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/>
PREFIX up: <http://purl.uniprot.org/core/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?organism ?taxon_commonname ?anatomicalentity ?anatomicalentityName ?gene_label ?anatomicalentity_label ?taxon_scientificname ?gene ?taxon WHERE { 
	?gene a orth:Gene .
	?gene genex:isExpressedIn ?anatomicalentity. # is expressed in
	?gene rdfs:label "APOC1" .
	?anatomicalentity a genex:AnatomicalEntity .
	?anatomicalentity rdfs:label ?anatomicalentityName .
	### Specifying species:
	?gene orth:organism ?organism . # in organism
	?organism obo:RO_0002162  ?taxon . # in taxon
	?taxon a up:Taxon .
	?taxon up:scientificName "Homo sapiens" .
	?taxon <http://purl.uniprot.org/core/scientificName> ?taxon_scientificname.
	?taxon <http://purl.uniprot.org/core/commonName> ?taxon_commonname.
	?anatomicalentity <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> ?anatomicalentity_label.
	?gene <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> ?gene_label.
}

PREFIX orth: <http://purl.org/net/orth#>
PREFIX genex: <http://purl.org/genex#>
PREFIX obo: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/>
PREFIX up: <http://purl.uniprot.org/core/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?organism ?stage ?expressioncondition ?taxon_commonname ?anatomicalentity ?score ?expression ?anatomicalentityName ?expression_hasfalsediscoveryratep_value ?strain ?gene_identifier ?anatomicalentity_label ?taxon_scientificname ?gene ?anatomicalentity_description ?expression_hasexpressionlevelscore ?taxon WHERE { 
	?gene a orth:Gene .
	?expression a genex:Expression .
	?expression genex:hasExpressionCondition ?expressioncondition . # has an expression condition
	?expression genex:hasExpressionLevel ?score .
	?expression genex:hasSequenceUnit ?gene . # has sequence unit
	?gene rdfs:label "APOC1" .
	?expressioncondition a genex:ExpressionCondition.
	?expressioncondition genex:hasAnatomicalEntity ?anatomicalentity . # has anatomical entity
	?expressioncondition genex:hasAnatomicalEntity obo:GO_0005575 . # has anatomical entity
	?anatomicalentity a genex:AnatomicalEntity.
	?anatomicalentity rdfs:label ?anatomicalentityName .
	?expressioncondition genex:hasDevelopmentalStage ?stage . # has a developmental stage
	?stage rdfs:label "post-juvenile" .
	?expressioncondition genex:hasSex "any".
	?expressioncondition genex:hasStrain ?strain . # has strain
	?strain rdfs:label "wild-type" .
	?gene orth:organism ?organism . # in organism
	?organism obo:RO_0002162  ?taxon . # in taxon
	?taxon a up:Taxon .
	?taxon up:commonName "human" .
	?taxon <http://purl.uniprot.org/core/scientificName> ?taxon_scientificname.
	?taxon <http://purl.uniprot.org/core/commonName> ?taxon_commonname.
	?anatomicalentity <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> ?anatomicalentity_label.
	?anatomicalentity <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> ?anatomicalentity_description.
	?expression <http://purl.org/genex#hasExpressionLevel> ?expression_hasexpressionlevelscore.
	?expression <http://purl.org/genex#hasFDRpvalue> ?expression_hasfalsediscoveryratep_value.
	?gene <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> ?gene_identifier.
	FILTER(               ?anatomicalentity !=  obo:GO_0005575               )
}

orth: <http://purl.org/net/orth#>
PREFIX genex: <http://purl.org/genex#>
PREFIX obo: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/>
PREFIX up: <http://purl.uniprot.org/core/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?taxon_commonname ?score ?expression ?falseDiscoveryRateP_value ?anatomicalentity_label ?gene_identifier ?anatomicalentity ?taxon_scientificname ?gene ?anatomicalentity_description ?expression_hasfalsediscoveryratep_value ?taxon WHERE { 
	?gene a orth:Gene .
	?expression a genex:Expression .
	?expression genex:hasExpressionCondition ?anatomicalentity . # has an expression condition
	?expression genex:hasExpressionLevel ?score .
	?expression genex:hasSequenceUnit ?gene . # has sequence unit
	?gene rdfs:label "APOC1" .
	?anatomicalentity a genex:AnatomicalEntity .
	?expression genex:hasAnatomicalEntity ?anatomicalentity . # has anatomical entity
	?anatomicalentity rdfs:label ?anatomicalentity_label .
	?expression genex:hasAnatomicalEntity obo:GO_0005575 . # has anatomical entity
	?anatomicalentity a genex:AnatomicalEntity.
	?expression genex:hasAnatomicalEntity obo:GO_0005575 . # has anatomical entity
	?anatomicalentity rdfs:label "cell" .
	?expression genex:hasDevelopmentalStage ?anatomicalentity . # has a developmental stage
	?anatomicalentity genex:isJuvenile ?falseDiscoveryRateP_value . # is a juvenile
	?anatomicalentity genex:isPostJuvenile ?expression . # is a post-juvenile
	?expression genex:hasSex "any".
	?expression genex:hasStrain ?taxon . # has strain
	?taxon a obo:RO_0002162  ?taxon_scientificname .
	?taxon <http://purl.uniprot.org/core/scientificName> ?taxon_commonname.
	?anatomicalentity <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> ?anatomicalentity_description.
	?expression <http://purl.org/genex#hasExpressionLevel> ?expression_hasfalsediscoveryratep_value.
	?gene <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> ?gene_identifier.
	FILTER(           ?anatomicalentity !=  obo:GO_0005575           )
}
ORDER BY ?anatomicalentity ?expression ?score ?gene ?anatomicalentity_label ?taxon_scientificname ?taxon_commonname ?expression ?anatomicalentity ?gene ?expression_hasfalsediscoveryratep_value ?taxon

PREFIX lscr: <http://purl.org/lscr#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?expressioncondition ?anatomicalentity ?score ?expression ?anatomicalentityName ?efo_0005135 ?gene_description ?gene WHERE { 
	?gene a orth:Gene .
	?expression a genex:Expression .
	?expression genex:hasExpressionCondition ?expressioncondition . # has an expression condition
	?expression genex:hasExpressionLevel ?score .
	?expression genex:hasSequenceUnit ?gene . # has sequence unit
	?gene lscr:xrefEnsemblGene ensembl:ENSG00000130208 .
	?expressioncondition a genex:ExpressionCondition.
	?expressioncondition genex:hasAnatomicalEntity ?anatomicalentity . # has anatomical entity
	?anatomicalentity a genex:AnatomicalEntity.
	?anatomicalentity rdfs:label ?anatomicalentityName .
	?expressioncondition genex:hasDevelopmentalStage obo:UBERON_0000113 . # has a developmental stage
	?expressioncondition genex:hasSex "any".
	?expressioncondition genex:hasStrain ?efo_0005135 . # has strain
	?efo_0005135 a efo:EFO_0005135.
	?efo_0005135 rdfs:label "wild-type" .
	?gene <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> ?gene_description.
	FILTER(   ?anatomicalentity !=  obo:GO_0005575   )
}
